OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779188576
OL,3,CPupil at Reading primary school being
OL,4,Ctreated for meningitis, the UKHSA
OL,5,Cconfirms
OL,7,FA primary school pupil in Reading is
OL,8,Fbeing treated for meningitis, it's
OL,9,Fbeen confirmed.
OL,11,FThe UK Health Security Agency said on
OL,12,FTuesday that a pupil at Westwood Farm
OL,13,FJunior School was diagnosed and is
OL,14,Frecovering well in hospital.
OL,16,FIt comes after a sixth form student
OL,17,Fdied from the disease last week, and
OL,18,Ftwo others were being treated at the
OL,19,FRoyal Berkshire Hospital.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
