PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779188576
OL,3,CPupil at Reading primary school being
OL,4,Ctreated for meningitis, the UKHSA
OL,5,Cconfirms
OL,7,FDr Rachel Mearkle, consultant in
OL,8,Fhealth protection, said: "A fourth
OL,9,Fcase of meningococcal disease has been
OL,10,Fconfirmed in Reading.
OL,12,F"This fourth case has links with the
OL,13,Fsame wider social network as the other
OL,14,Fcases, where measures, including
OL,15,Fantibiotic prophylaxis, have already
OL,16,Fbeen implemented.
OL,18,F"The individual, who attends Westwood
OL,19,FFarm Junior School, is recovering well.
OL,26,@pD@ZOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
