OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1779188576
OL,3,CPupil at Reading primary school being
OL,4,Ctreated for meningitis, the UKHSA
OL,5,Cconfirms
OL,7,F"Information has been shared with
OL,8,Fparents and carers at the school to
OL,9,Fadvise of the signs and symptoms to
OL,10,Flook out for.
OL,12,F"All four cases have been confirmed to
OL,13,Fbe Meningitis B (MenB).
OL,15,F"The risk to the wider public remains
OL,16,Flow and this case is not linked to the
OL,17,Fincidents in Kent or Dorset."
OL,19,FThis is the fourth case of meningitis
OL,20,Fconfirmed in the area following an
OL,21,Foutbreak last week.
OL,26,@yD@]O]
