OL,3,CPupil at Reading primary school being
OL,4,Ctreated for meningitis, the UKHSA
OL,5,Cconfirms
OL,7,FHenley College sixth form student
OL,8,FLewis Waters passed away just hours
OL,9,Fafter developing sepsis.
OL,11,FTwo other students- one from Reading
OL,12,FBlue Coat School in Sonning, and
OL,13,Fanother from Highdown School in Emmer
OL,14,FGreen are being treated at the Royal
OL,15,FBerkshire Hospital in Reading.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
